<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(قد بعثنَا بفراش ... فاهجرن وَجه الْمصلى)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(ووصلناه بغيداء ... كبدر يتجلى)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(فتفضل بِقبُول ... لَا عدمت الدَّهْر فضلا)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(وورا ذَلِك منى ... سترى فضلا وفضلا)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
